      <title>瑞士坚持银行资本计划 瑞银受挫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/switzerland-will-stick-to-schedule-on-new-bank-capital-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士表示，尽管美国对标准问题的争论持续不断，但瑞士仍将按照计划实施全球银行资本规则，这可能会使其最大的银行瑞银集团 (UBS Group AG) 处于竞争劣势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/switzerland-will-stick-to-schedule-on-new-bank-capital-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 08:03:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
